\f0\b \cf0 Product Overview
\f1\b0 \
Witness R.E.P is a free, encrypted civil rights Progressive Web App designed to protect people during police encounters, arrests, and public incidents. The app automatically encrypts footage, generates tamper proof legal certificates, sends SOS alerts to trusted contacts, and enables livestreaming to nearby users. It requires no subscription, contains no ads, and is built on the principle that protecting yourself should never cost money.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Problem Statement
\f1\b0 \
Every year thousands of people record incidents of police misconduct, wrongful arrests, and civil rights violations on their phones. The footage is deleted by officers, destroyed when phones are seized, dismissed in court for lack of metadata, or simply never reaches a lawyer in time. The people who need protection the most have the fewest tools to protect their evidence.\
Existing apps like ACLU Mobile Justice are limited to 18 states and lack cryptographic verification. Citizen costs $19.99 per month and prioritizes alerts over evidence. No app on the market combines instant recording, military grade encryption, tamper proof legal certificates, and real time SOS alerts in one free tool.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Target Users
\f1\b0 \
Primary users are people in high risk interactions with law enforcement including traffic stops, arrests, protests, and street encounters. Secondary users are civil rights lawyers, investigative journalists, legal observers, and community organizations who need verified digital evidence.\
The initial focus is New York City with expansion to all 50 states and eventually global markets.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Core Value Proposition
\f1\b0 \
Witness R.E.P is not a recording app. It is a truth machine. Every recording generates a cryptographically verified Witness Certificate that proves the footage was never altered, making it court admissible evidence from the moment the record button is pressed.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

