\f0\b \cf0 Feature Requirements
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Must have for launch, P0:
\f1\b0 \
Camera opens instantly on app launch with no loading screen or navigation required. Recording starts with one tap and stops with one tap. Video is encrypted with AES-256-GCM before saving. SHA-256 hash is generated for every recording. GPS coordinates, timestamp, and device ID are embedded in metadata. Witness Certificate PDF is generated automatically after every recording. Public verify page allows anyone to confirm a certificate is authentic. S3 cloud upload begins simultaneously with recording. SOS sends SMS to trusted contacts with GPS location and watch link. Livestream via Mux with GO LIVE button. Map shows active streams and public recordings. Phone and email authentication via Supabase. Vault is PIN protected. PWA is installable from browser. App works on both iPhone and Android.\

\f0\b Should have for launch, P1:
\f1\b0 \
Decoy PIN system with two isolated encrypted vaults. Know Your Rights screen for all 50 states. Incident categories for recordings. Feedback button. Biometric unlock. Emergency detained button triggering recording SOS and location simultaneously. Automatic state detection showing rights reminder on open. Front and back camera switch. Flash toggle.\

\f0\b Nice to have for launch, P2:
\f1\b0 \
Audio only recording mode. Timestamp watermark on exported video. Auto transcription. Evidence package export bundle. Witness network. Community alert system. Safe corridor with auto SOS. Scheduled check in.\

\f0\b Future, P3:
\f1\b0 \
Apple Watch integration. Capacitor native wrapper for App Store. Background recording. Mesh networking. Zero knowledge architecture. International expansion. AI transcription with key phrase flagging.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

